        <title>Hugo Theme Submission Validation Script</title>
        <link>https://mansoorbarri.com/downloads/hugo-validator/</link>
        <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://mansoorbarri.com/downloads/hugo-validator/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;I have been developing multiple Hugo themes with the intention of getting it on the &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://themes.gohugo.io&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Hugo themes page&lt;/a&gt; however, despite having the experience of doing this multiple times, I get something wrong everytime. So I decided to make a script which goes through the important things which are required to submit your theme on their site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some things include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Absolute links&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Author information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Licence information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Theme version&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can learn more here: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/mansoorbarri/hugo-validator/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/mansoorbarri/hugo-validator/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;usage&#34;&gt;Usage&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Make sure you have &lt;code&gt;python&lt;/code&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;code&gt;git&lt;/code&gt; installed on your system before using the tool.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clone the script: &lt;code&gt;git clone https://github.com/mansoorbarri/hugo-validator &amp;amp;&amp;amp; cd hugo-validator&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;install the requirements: &lt;code&gt;pip3 install -r requirements.txt&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run the validator: &lt;code&gt;python3 validator.py&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;you might have to run the validator with &lt;code&gt;python&lt;/code&gt; instead of &lt;code&gt;python3&lt;/code&gt; especially in Windows.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;contributions&#34;&gt;Contributions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want want more things to be validate by the script or have a better way to do this, feel free to send a PR over on GitHub.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;compiled-file&#34;&gt;Compiled File&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is &lt;strong&gt;no&lt;/strong&gt; standalone file for Windows or Mac however, it will come later down the line. Right now its a simple script so it doesn&amp;rsquo;t make sense to have a compiled file for it in my opinion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
</description>
        </item>
        <item>
        <title>Glim Midnight Hugo theme</title>
        <link>https://mansoorbarri.com/downloads/glim-midnight/</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 17 Nov 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://mansoorbarri.com/downloads/glim-midnight/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mansoorbarri/glim-midnight/main/images/screenshot.png&#34;
	
	
	
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;screenshot of the example site&#34;
	
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Minimal version of linktree or &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/jpanther/lynx&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Hugo Lynx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;authors&#34;&gt;Authors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://mansoorbarri.com/&#34; &gt;Mansoor Barri&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://maheenwaris.com&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Maheen Waris&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customizable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dark&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bootstrap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Light version (coming soon)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SEO friendly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;wiki&#34;&gt;Wiki&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wiki page can be found here: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/mansoorbarri/glim-midnight/wiki&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;https://github.com/mansoorbarri/glim-midnight/wiki&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;setup&#34;&gt;Setup&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make a new hugo site&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;hugo new site {sitename}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clone the theme in themes folder&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markdown&#34; data-lang=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;cd {sitename}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git clone &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;https:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;//&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;github&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;mansoorbarri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;coming-soon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;git&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; themes/coming-soon
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;or you can use &lt;code&gt;submodule&lt;/code&gt; if you already have GitHub repository for your website&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markdown&#34; data-lang=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git init
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git submodule add &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;https:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;//&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;github&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;mansoorbarri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;glim-midnight&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;git&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; themes/glim-midnight
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Copy &lt;code&gt;examplesite/config.toml&lt;/code&gt; files to yours for quick setup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open &lt;code&gt;config.toml&lt;/code&gt; and edit as per your liking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;configtoml&#34;&gt;Config.toml&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 7
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 8
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 9
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;10
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;11
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;12
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;13
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;14
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;15
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;baseURL = &amp;#34;&amp;lt;http://glim-midnight.pages.dev&amp;gt;&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;languageCode = &amp;#34;en-us&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;theme = &amp;#34;glim-midnight&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;[params]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    title = &amp;#34;Glim Midnight&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    phrases = [&amp;#34;Bootstrap&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;Dark&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;Minimal&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;Responsive&amp;#34;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    links = [
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    {name = &amp;#34;Github&amp;#34;, url = &amp;#34;&amp;lt;https://github.com/mansoorbarri/glim-midnight/&amp;#34;},
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    {name = &amp;#34;Wiki&amp;#34;, url = &amp;#34;/wiki&amp;#34;},
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    {name = &amp;#34;Author I&amp;#34;, url = &amp;#34;&amp;lt;https://maheenwaris.com/&amp;gt;&amp;#34;},
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    {name = &amp;#34;Author II&amp;#34;, url = &amp;#34;&amp;lt;https://mansoorbarri.com/&amp;gt;&amp;#34;},
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    {name = &amp;#34;Hugo&amp;#34;, url = &amp;#34;&amp;lt;https://gohugo.io/&amp;gt;&amp;#34;},
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    ]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    background = &amp;#34;bg.mp4&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Variables you should/can change&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;baseURL&lt;/code&gt;: URL of your website&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;title&lt;/code&gt;: this title will be shown as tab name and as &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;h1&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; on this website&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;phrases&lt;/code&gt;: these are the words which are animated under the main title&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;links&lt;/code&gt;: these are the links you want to add, you have to mention the name &amp;amp; the url where the button will lead to&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;background&lt;/code&gt;: this is the background of the webpage currently, the theme only supports video as a background.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;the default location of the background is in &lt;code&gt;/assets/&lt;/code&gt;, it is recommended to use the same folder for a custom background.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;things-to-note&#34;&gt;Things to note&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If you want to add your email in one as one of the links, add “mailto:” before the email address in &lt;code&gt;url&lt;/code&gt; something like this:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-markdown&#34; data-lang=&#34;markdown&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;{name = &amp;#34;Email&amp;#34;, url = &amp;#34;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;mailto:uname&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;example&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#34;},
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;the default location of the background is in &lt;code&gt;/assets/&lt;/code&gt;, it is recommended to use the same folder for a custom background.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
